{"tid":636317,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【玩具迷之死】玩具兵團如另類兵馬桶！ 25萬件藏品要搵新主人","createTime":"2018-04-20T17:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T07:12:43.000Z","uid":36494,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"dca98760fb3191fddc3fdc793d256d9b282a6f58","tid":636317,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:36:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180421&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58096188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180421%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58096188&d=rmQRCwUQjDIqh2s8OWqFuhxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=40c1e05b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180421%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58096188&h=84b44edc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180421&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58096188</a><br />\n<br />\n【玩具迷之死】玩具兵團如另類兵馬桶！ 25萬件藏品要搵新主人<br />\n<br />\n英國布里斯托爾一名玩具收藏家患白血病逝世，他自孩童時代便開始收集士玩具士兵、飛機及一切配件，收藏品高達25萬件。拍賣公司本月底會將這批收藏進行拍賣，形容這是全英甚至全球有史以來最大規模拍賣。<br />\n<br />\n55歲的馬佐達（Carmelo Mazzotta）將大量玩具收藏放在一個車房內，車房地板不但鋪滿玩具，四周亦放置了4個架子，甚至連車房閣樓都放滿玩具，天花板更懸掛了一系列壓鑄（die-cast）模型飛機。<br />\n<br />\n馬佐達的收藏品包括不少以鉛、金屬、塑膠物料製造的士兵，士兵介乎2.5至5厘米（1至2吋）高，但有一些尺寸更大；他生前亦收藏了如城堡、武器、飛機及樹等配件。<br />\n<br />\n拍賣公司要派出兩名員工，花了整整9天才將所有玩具及配件打包入箱搬回陳列室，而且由於玩具數量實在太多，拍賣公司更要徵用平日用作儲物的地方存放。<br />\n<br />\n有關拍賣會於本月27及28日舉行，負責拍賣的Wessex Auction Rooms玩具部門負責人威克斯（Tim Weeks）形容，這是英國甚至最大規模的玩具士兵收藏，估計會以逾一萬鎊（11萬港元）成交。<br />\n<br />\n威克斯續稱：「這是馬佐達一生的興趣，賣掉它們對其家人來說感觸良多&hellip;&hellip;除非你真的全身全意投入精力，否則你無法累積這樣的收藏品。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/013630_a797d315faebced6bd748fd139f0cdaa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F013630_a797d315faebced6bd748fd139f0cdaa.png&h=5dc73319&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/013631_9cb7ec45cf1a85fb2578298b28ccbc80.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F013631_9cb7ec45cf1a85fb2578298b28ccbc80.png&h=d057f4f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/013634_d695aced5fa3f187daf3c99ae4aa138a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F013634_d695aced5fa3f187daf3c99ae4aa138a.png&h=ba08a1e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/013637_4d4a6946c15d5a37500efe4e711f9b24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F013637_4d4a6946c15d5a37500efe4e711f9b24.png&h=beac8304&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/013640_06eb518bbe49a94a9635067e72449931.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F013640_06eb518bbe49a94a9635067e72449931.png&h=2ef2d235&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"330840b802a530deaf9936741ba75bd1aef59eb1","tid":636317,"uid":164913,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e2e0286d3e2dac13e658740c0103c607faa0fcc","tid":636317,"uid":121885,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:41:23.000Z","msg":"兵乜L野馬桶<br />\n<br />\n放入屎坑玩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ba17dd32f6128873f3f68d9247263f6bcb06ff","tid":636317,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:42:28.000Z","msg":"布里斯托爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6636fb79e06357f53d4f8765